These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, fonseca, prince, tiparillo
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, daffodil, tulip, dahlia
4 different games are played: whist, poker, backgammon, go
1. the person playing whist is the tiparillo-smoker##1
2. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
3. the tiparillo-smoker is in an odd position##4
4. the person playing poker is on the left or right of the person playing go##3
5. the person who growstulip is on the left or right of the game-smoker##3
6. the person playing go is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
7. the person playing poker is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person playing go is between the person who growsdahlia and the game-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| Cigar         | tiparillo      | game | fonseca | prince |
| Flower   | tulip | daisy  | daffodil   | dahlia    |
| Game     | whist     | backgammon    | go    | poker      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-2::.
4 different games are played: go, billiard, backgammon, monopoly
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, musical, superhero, crime
House: farmhouse, townhouse, art-deco, cottage
1. the townhouse house is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
2. the person playing monopoly is the person watching superhero movies##1
3. the person playing backgammon is in an even position##4
4. the farmhouse house is on the far right##1
5. the cottage house is on the far left##1
6. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
7. the person watching drama movies is between the person playing monopoly and the person playing billiard##2
8. the person watching crime movies is between the person watching musical movies and the person playing backgammon##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Game         | monopoly | backgammon   | billiard | go  |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero     | drama | crime  | musical |
| House     | cottage        | art-deco  | townhouse    | farmhouse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-3::.
4 different pets are kept: frog, hamster, ferret, goat
House: tower, craftsman, colonial, farmhouse
The people have 4 different jobs:  social-worker, dressmaker, security-guard, freelancer
1. the farmhouse house is between the owner of the frog and the owner of the goat##2
2. the craftsman house is the freelancer##1
3. the social-worker is the owner of the ferret##1
4. the social-worker is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
5. the owner of the goat is in an odd position##4
6. the colonial house is between the owner of the hamster and the tower house##2
7. the farmhouse house is on the left of the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Pet          | frog | hamster   | goat     | ferret     |
| House   | craftsman  | farmhouse | colonial   | tower  |
| Job     | freelancer      | dressmaker | security-guard | social-worker |

