.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, chinese, argentine, indonesian
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, fonseca, aristoff, montecristo
4 different games are played: domino, go, monopoly, scrabble
1. the montecristo-smoker is in an even position##4
2. the chinese is the person playing go##1
3. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person playing domino##1
4. the fonseca-smoker is on the left or right of the argentine##3
5. the montecristo-smoker is the person playing domino##1
6. the argentine is the cain-smoker##1
7. the aristoff-smoker is the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Nationality   | turkish  | indonesian   | argentine     | chinese |
| Cigar   | aristoff  | montecristo      | cain        | fonseca     |
| Game         | monopoly | domino | scrabble | go   |

