.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: ebony, coral, turquise, grey
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, daisy, marigold, lily
City: nizza, berlin, san-francisco, edinburgh
1. the person who likes grey is the person who growslily##1
2. the person who likes turquise is in an odd position##4
3. the person traveling to nizza is the person who growslily##1
4. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person who growslily##1
5. the person traveling to nizza is in an even position##4
6. the person who growsdaisy is on the far left##1
7. the person who likes coral is on the far right##1
8. the person who likes turquise is on the left or right of the person traveling to san-francisco##3
9. the person who growstulip is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Color   | ebony   | grey   | turquise | coral |
| Flower         | daisy      | lily | tulip      | marigold |
| City     | berlin | nizza        | edinburgh       | san-francisco  |

