.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
House: art-deco, modern, gothic-revival, cape-cod
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, water-polo, golf, rowing
The people have 4 different jobs:  musician, analyst, pilot, paramedic
1. the modern house is in an odd position##4
2. the pilot is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
3. the musician is the modern house##1
4. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the analyst##1
5. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the far right##1
6. the cape-cod house is on the left of the modern house##1
7. the cape-cod house is in an even position##4
8. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| House    | gothic-revival   | cape-cod      | modern       | art-deco |
| Sport   | surfing | rowing | golf     | water-polo |
| Job     | paramedic     | analyst  | musician | pilot |

