.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, climbing, weightlifting, tennis
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, van, scooter, car
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, malaysian, pakistani, german
1. the pakistani is the person driving the skateboard##1
2. the malaysian is between the person driving the car and the mexican##2
3. the person driving the car is the person who's sport is climbing##1
4. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person who's sport is climbing##3
5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is in an even position##4
6. the person driving the car is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
7. the person driving the skateboard is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
8. the pakistani is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Sport      | weightlifting   | tennis          | climbing | skateboarding        |
| Transport   | scooter     | van | car   | skateboard     |
| Nationality           | mexican | malaysian         | german         | pakistani |

