.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, roller, helicopter, boat
House: wooden, craftsman, cape-cod, cottage
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, amaryllis, poppy, marigold
1. the person who growsmarigold is on the left or right of the person who growspoppy##3
2. the cape-cod house is the person driving the subway##1
3. the cottage house is the person driving the helicopter##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
5. the person who growsamaryllis is between the wooden house and the person driving the subway##2
6. the person who growsmarigold is on the left or right of the cape-cod house##3
7. the person driving the subway is in an even position##4
8. the person driving the subway is between the person driving the roller and the person driving the helicopter##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Transport         | roller | subway      | helicopter       | boat    |
| House           | craftsman  | cape-cod  | cottage | wooden |
| Flower   | marigold      | poppy | amaryllis         | balloon-flower    |

