.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, begonia, dahlia, iris
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, musical, adventure, spy
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, chess, collecting, fishing
1. the person watching disaster movies is in an odd position##4
2. the person who growsbellflower is on the left or right of the person watching disaster movies##3
3. the person who growsiris is on the left or right of the person watching disaster movies##3
4. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
5. the person who growsbegonia is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
6. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
7. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
8. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
9. the person watching spy movies is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Flower   | begonia         | bellflower  | dahlia     | iris         |
| Movie-Genre        | spy | musical | disaster | adventure         |
| Hobby      | chess         | collecting  | puzzles   | fishing |

