.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
House: wooden, palace, colonial, art-deco
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, filmmaking, drawing, hiking
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, subway, jet-ski, scooter
 1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the colonial house##3
 2. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person driving the subway is on the right of the palace house##1
 4. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the palace house and the wooden house##2
 5. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the palace house##3
 6. the person driving the scooter is the colonial house##1
 7. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far right##1
 8. the wooden house is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the art-deco house and the colonial house##2
10. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| House   | wooden  | colonial    | palace | art-deco    |
| Hobby   | traveling | drawing | filmmaking  | hiking |
| Transport           | jet-ski   | scooter    | helicopter        | subway   |

