.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
4 different games are played: bridge, billiard, domino, poker
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, gardening, drawing, filmmaking
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, oliveros, fonseca, siglo
1. the person playing bridge is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
3. the siglo-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is drawing##3
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an even position##4
5. the person playing domino is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
6. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
7. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
8. the person playing poker is on the left or right of the oliveros-smoker##3
9. the person playing bridge is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Game      | bridge                | poker  | billiard | domino   |
| Hobby           | filmmaking | gardening | rock-climbing   | drawing |
| Cigar   | oliveros         | bolivar     | siglo     | fonseca |

