4. the indonesian is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
5. the person playing poker is between the person who's hobby is dancing and the person playing monopoly##2
6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an even position##4
7. the chinese is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Nationality          | indonesian    | dutch  | french  | chinese |
| Hobby   | dancing | baking | board-games | sudoku |
| Game   | domino    | poker     | monopoly    | bridge |

