.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, epic, satire, family
4 different games are played: poker, snooker, go, domino
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, traveling, writing, magic-tricks
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is between the person watching satire movies and the person playing poker##2
2. the person watching horror movies is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person playing go is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3
4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in an odd position##4
6. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3
7. the person playing poker is on the left or right of the person playing domino##3
8. the person playing go is the person watching horror movies##1
9. the person playing domino is between the person who's hobby is writing and the person who's hobby is camping##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Movie-Genre      | horror | satire      | epic  | family    |
| Game   | go   | snooker | domino | poker |
| Hobby           | magic-tricks      | writing       | traveling   | camping      |

