.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-14::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, country, d&b, indie
There are 4 different favourite colors: coral, red, blue, lavender
4 different pets are kept: hamster, turtle, pony, hedgehog
1. the fan of d&b is in an even position##4
2. the fan of country is between the fan of indie and the owner of the hamster##2
3. the owner of the turtle is on the far left or far right##3
4. the fan of indie is in an even position##4
5. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
6. the person who likes lavender is between the owner of the hamster and the person who likes coral##2
7. the owner of the turtle is on the far right##1
8. the person who likes red is in an even position##4
9. the owner of the hamster is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Music-Genre         | house    | d&b | country  | indie  |
| Color   | blue | red       | lavender | coral |
| Pet         | pony   | hamster      | hedgehog | turtle       |

