4. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
6. the person who's sport is baseball is in an odd position##4
7. the person traveling to london is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person playing poker##1

.:: Answer ::.
